        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜ 油不是80年代 油價升至24年以來新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 油不是80年代 油價升至24年以來新高\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EmQCsZfaNoWyVkxE3pBSNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/b9d50650-18e1-11f1-bfef-b60337aaa5bd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 油不是80年代 油價升至24年以來新高</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周四收市下跌，華爾街未能延續前一交易日的反彈走勢。中東衝突持續成為市場焦點，同時油價再度急升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指盤中一度大跌1100點，收市下跌約1.6%，即逾780點；標普500指數下跌約0.6%；科技權重較高的納斯達克綜合指數跌幅較小，下跌 0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場仍聚焦中東局勢。美國與以色列聯盟與伊朗之間的攻擊已蔓延至區內多地。周四為衝突爆發第六日，暫未見緩和跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗為石油輸出國組織第四大產油國，其產能受損對大宗商品及股市均帶來廣泛影響，市場憂慮油價急升，或迫使聯儲局在波動的市場環境下重新評估利率政策。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b7d9a1de-0752-4ae2-b7e9-d9f75e0dc5ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價再次上揚，布蘭特原油期貨觸2024 年以來最高水平，預料將進一步推高汽油價格。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月5日（星期四）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 跌784.67點或1.61%，報47,954.74點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 跌38.79點或0.56%，報6,830.71點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌58.5點或0.26%，報22,748.99點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期油</ins></a> 收報78.87元一桶，升4.21美元或5.64%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報5,093.3美元一盎司，跌41.4美元或0.81%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報71,248.12美元，跌1,862.51美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.146厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國2月28日初次申領失業救濟人數為21.3萬，與上期持平。預期為21.5萬。市場關注周五公布的每月就業報告，該數據將為投資者提供勞動市場健康狀況的最新線索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指大跌，傳統股受壓，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:波音;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BA/\">波音</a>(BA.US)跌2.3%、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Caterpillar;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CAT/\">Caterpillar</a>(CAT.US)挫3.5%。銀行股<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩通;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/JPM/\">摩通</a>(JPM.US)、摩根士丹利(MS.US)跌2%至3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:甲骨文;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/ORCL/\">甲骨文</a>(ORCL.US)計劃裁減數千名員工，以應對大規模人工智能數據中心擴張帶來的資金短缺而採取的措施之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Costco;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/COST/\">Costco</a>(COST.US)收市後公布業績，第二財季每股盈利4.58美元，略高於預期的4.55美元；收入為696億美元，高於預期的693億美元。 經調整同店銷售額按年增長6.7%，預期增長為6.3%。盤後Costco微跌。</p></div>",
